Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.99,0:00:05.34,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}From the me of yesterday, to the me of tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.78,0:00:09.46,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please don't mind the missing pages in the diary.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.56,0:00:12.44,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There were mistakes, so it was ripped out and thrown away, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.64,0:00:15.49,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's absolutely not because there was some kind of misfortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.68,0:00:17.53,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Rather because  it was something happy. {memory}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.75,0:00:21.13,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It was such happiness that was too good for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.52,0:00:24.57,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And so, this is wrongly written. {or wrongly written}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.78,0:00:27.14,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It is something that didn't happen in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.17,0:00:29.20,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So it was ripped out.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.43,0:00:33.09,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please don't mind and continue like you have now everyday.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.10,0:00:33.75,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.43,0:00:37.54,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Also, with the person named Asou Renji,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.54,0:00:39.89,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}please do not get involved with him anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.91,0:00:44.62,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It will bring misfortune to him, and yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.96,0:00:48.02,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To the me of tomorrow, from the me of yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.22,0:03:28.43,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After parting with Chihiro, the time that had passed had been much more than thirteen hours. {can anyone word this better?}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.20,0:03:32.93,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Chihiro must have... forgotten all about what happened yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.59,0:03:35.34,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Not only about the things that happened yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.73,0:03:38.25,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but everything from after the day she met me.{the memory}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.99,0:03:41.40,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}About me... everything... {again, the memory}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.56,0:03:56.58,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro is the same as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.24,0:04:01.07,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,The same as always, just like Chihiro was before she met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.02,0:04:05.87,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Why did she wrote that kind of story? Do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.76,0:04:10.13,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,If you have something to say, I'll listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.90,0:04:13.96,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I see. It's painful, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.32,0:04:17.04,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't say comforting things.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.52,0:04:22.15,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise, it seems like it really ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.21,0:04:23.83,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It really did end.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.81,0:04:27.37,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,To put Chihiro's symptoms specifically,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.37,0:04:29.36,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,it's not that she's forgetting what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.55,0:04:31.93,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,The memory in the brain itself disappears.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.45,0:04:37.11,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's like a memo that disappears in thirteen hours, which is repetitively lost. {check}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.17,0:04:42.37,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,With today's medical science, Chihiro's condition cannot be cured.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.58,0:04:44.67,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it is cured from a miracle,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.25,0:04:48.04,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,the memo that vanished once does not return ever again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.92,0:04:51.04,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.17,0:04:54.78,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,In this kind of world, miracles do not exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.89,0:04:56.91,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,What exists are coincidence and the inevitable.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.91,0:04:59.68,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Then from there is what oneself does, and that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.63,0:05:04.43,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,To not be able to reach your hand to your loved one is painful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.82,0:05:06.97,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,But if it's connected continuously, {check}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.97,0:05:09.06,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,the heart will be continuously weighed down by the burden. {check}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.29,0:05:12.49,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,But, it isn't something that can be forgotten just because of that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.68,0:05:14.24,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't say to forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.65,0:05:19.49,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,To live carrying that burden{weight}, is one of the ways of living.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.00,0:05:22.53,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I won't say that you should live like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.00,0:05:28.11,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Can I ask just one thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.11,0:05:28.92,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.09,0:05:31.57,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,The reason why Himura-san is always at the church...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.69,0:05:34.09,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,is because of having to carry that burden?{weight} {Renji just ends the question there, and I didn't really put the question mark}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.18,0:05:36.49,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows... I've forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.60,0:05:45.66,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.20,0:05:49.19,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?{What is it?}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.28,0:05:52.10,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing much, just wondering what's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.10,0:05:53.43,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.43,0:05:58.19,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Really? And also, isn't it about time to submit the future career survey? {check}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.42,0:05:59.27,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.28,0:06:01.46,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Did you decide on what you want to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.47,0:06:03.19,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,No, not yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.19,0:06:05.70,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so? Well, take your time to think about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.70,0:06:07.59,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,since it is Renji's dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.70,0:06:08.43,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's not possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.55,0:06:09.60,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? {Not sure if I should put this, I'll leave it upto the others}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.60,0:06:11.86,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I can only think about tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.86,0:06:13.57,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,With such talk of the future...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.41,0:06:16.66,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,a thing like tomorrow can't exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.83,0:06:17.95,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Renji...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.95,0:06:20.70,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,A thing like tomorrow, would be better if it never came. {can anyone word thsi better?}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.82,0:06:26.52,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't say things like that, as tomorrow might be better than today. {More like, "prepare today, as tomorrow might be worse then today"}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.73,0:06:30.94,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Renji? Where are you going?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.79,0:06:39.15,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps tomorrow will be even better than today?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.56,0:06:43.87,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,There is no way... it'll be like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.51,0:06:49.09,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,What are you so worked up about, young lad? {check}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.50,0:06:50.75,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Kuze-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.51,0:06:53.33,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.67,0:06:55.05,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for the trouble. {I was thinking of putting "Thank you," but it doesn't quite mean that so I put it like this. Feel free to change this anyone}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.49,0:07:00.22,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Humans are... cruel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.23,0:07:01.23,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm? {Should this be taken out?}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.23,0:07:05.07,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Even while being in such suffering, hunger, even sleepiness, you can still feel.{Even though being in such suffering, hunger is felt, feel sleepy even while suffering.}{check-whoa, major rewording needed...}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.16,0:07:12.63,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,And even when you eat or drink, you feel further suffering because of not being able to forgive oneself.{And, farther suffering because of not being able to forgive oneself that leisure drinks and eats while suffering.}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.65,0:07:15.61,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,But, that's proof of living.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.82,0:07:16.93,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Kuze-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.93,0:07:17.93,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?{What is it?}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.12,0:07:20.90,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,To make a dream come true, what do you have to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.99,0:07:25.87,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see, to make a dream come true, first the dream itself must exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.15,0:07:27.69,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,The dream itself?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.69,0:07:31.03,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It might seem obvious, but it's something important.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.13,0:07:35.86,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,The image of wanting things to be this way, or even things like memories are fine. {check}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.86,0:07:37.02,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.70,0:07:40.38,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,For me, that is this... {That's what he said. Stupid Kuze, trying to talk like a wise one making tl harder...}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.81,0:07:43.92,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Not forgetting that memory, and to go on with making more... {memories}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.04,0:07:46.14,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,That is the first step of making a dream come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.66,0:07:49.90,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,If... that thought is impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.91,0:07:51.98,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,then you can only wait for a miracle to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.67,0:07:54.85,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,"In this world, miracles do not exist."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.00,0:07:59.82,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,"What exists are coincidence and the inevitable."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.82,0:08:01.36,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,That's Himura's way of speaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.16,0:08:06.01,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,But at times, an action's result becomes the inevitable,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.02,0:08:10.46,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,and that combines with coincidence, to make a dream come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.96,0:08:13.88,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if that's a miracle or not,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.95,0:08:15.92,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,but there's one thing that's certain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.85,0:08:19.72,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,If there is no desire for it, nothing will happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.69,0:08:32.47,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Desire, huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.80,0:08:34.55,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even though I have a desire for it,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.55,0:08:36.23,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}there are some things I can't do anything about.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.67,0:08:39.96,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Chihiro's memory does not come back once it disappears.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.25,0:08:42.79,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The time that she has spent with me, has already... {disappeared}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.01,0:08:53.95,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I always felt like I wanted to cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.23,0:08:58.97,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Every time I looked up, tears would come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.27,0:09:00.58,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Chihiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.24,0:09:06.43,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Umm... {check}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.65,0:09:07.43,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.16,0:09:12.44,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Umm... Do you mind if I ask something a bit odd?{Umm... Is it okay for me to ask something odd?}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.63,0:09:16.56,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Are you... someone that I've met before?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.31,0:09:29.04,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I... still remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.65,0:09:35.42,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I still remember everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.88,0:09:37.58,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Those aren't things that can be forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.55,0:09:42.18,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,How... How can it be like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.28,0:10:36.54,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.16,0:10:39.98,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Soon I will part with Renji-kun."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.07,0:10:46.28,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Even though it'll be painful and lonely, it was decided from the beginning that it would end like this."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.36,0:10:47.94,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"So it doesn't matter."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.42,0:10:51.22,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because this would be the last time, I kissed a lot. {check}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.22,0:10:53.95,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because this would be the last time, I loved a lot.{check}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.03,0:10:58.34,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even though it's sad, this memory will also soon disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.57,0:11:01.99,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Still, I think it will definitely be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.05,0:11:03.75,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No matter how painful...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.76,0:11:05.50,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No matter how lonely...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.51,0:11:07.72,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I will forget soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.54,0:11:12.96,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But, it's very painful because I still remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.97,0:11:14.64,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's very painful.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.64,0:11:18.80,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Renji-kun's warmth is still in my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.28,0:11:22.96,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Truthfully, I want to stay with Renji-kun even now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.10,0:11:24.87,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I always want to feel Renji-kun's touch.{Ooooookay, someone please reword this...}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.30,0:11:28.18,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even now, I want to be with Renji-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.86,0:11:31.54,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't want to forget; I don't want to disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.54,0:11:34.74,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No longer do I want to go back to the days full of nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.50,0:11:40.13,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Renji-kun... was a knight that rescued me from the suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.66,0:11:46.68,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Renji-kun... was a prince that rescued me from the never-ending time. {check}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.06,0:11:49.84,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even though it's forgotten. {memory}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.84,0:11:51.38,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even though it disappears. {memory}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.51,0:11:54.89,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Still, I love Renji-kun very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.41,0:11:57.01,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No matter how much the time passes...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.20,0:11:59.62,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even though everything disappears from me,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.62,0:12:02.01,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I, as of this moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.01,0:12:04.91,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}love Renji-kun from the bottom of my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.32,0:12:08.28,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Renji-kun... Thank you very much for everything up to now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.98,0:12:11.49,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And... Goodbye...{This scene just rips your heart out...}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.67,0:12:28.93,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Still... There is something that can be done...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.48,0:12:30.97,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}even if it may be futile.{check}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.34,0:12:33.35,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But... But...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.41,0:13:49.46,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Even though it's not enough, even though it's far from enough...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.06,0:13:54.47,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I will put it together, I will surely put it all back together.{I'll assemble it, I'll surely assemble it all.}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.01,0:13:58.85,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,So... So about me...! {check}{god, I hate it when they use the subject first and cut out the rest, so hard to translate it.}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.94,0:14:02.35,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Thirteen hours... is a very long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.60,0:14:06.65,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you do such things?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.92,0:14:08.01,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.29,0:14:09.81,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Despite the fact that I shouldn't...{Despite the fact that it's prohibited}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.81,0:14:12.95,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Because with Renji-kun... I have to forget...{About Renji-kun... I have to forget.}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.29,0:14:18.40,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I've thought about it... over and over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.41,0:14:24.45,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's not possible... not possible at all... to not think about Renji-kun for thirteen hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.69,0:14:25.84,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.62,0:14:34.30,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry... I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.32,0:14:36.17,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you forget...{No longer will I let you forget.}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.51,0:14:39.89,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you forget anymore, no matter what happens.{I'll not allow you to forget, no matter what happens.}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.04,0:14:44.65,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I... am always with Chihiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.64,0:14:46.59,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.95,0:14:48.77,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.71,0:14:54.74,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Renji-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.98,0:14:55.99,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.79,0:15:04.92,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what, we'll always be together. {check}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.45,0:15:12.33,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, I think, pleads at least once to God...{Someone, I think have at least once pleaded to God.}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.37,0:15:14.72,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,even if without believing in anything. {religion}{I hate implicit subject...}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.72,0:15:19.30,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,The day when one prays with a true heart will eventually come.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.42,0:15:21.44,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Something that everyone is looking for...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.44,0:15:23.40,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Something that everyone wants...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.56,0:15:27.09,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Something that is made from circulating memories and the bonds{ties} between people...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.09,0:15:28.93,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,What is in front of that is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.71,0:15:53.96,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I said to leave the lock on the hard disc off, otherwise I can't edit it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.08,0:15:57.11,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,President, are you still insisting on that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.11,0:16:00.88,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it better just to give up and turn your attention to the new work?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.94,0:16:03.34,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine. Just let me do what I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.30,0:16:05.98,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It won't end this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.98,0:16:08.96,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,With the clips that he filmed, there's no way it'll end like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.48,0:16:15.20,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it is vexing, it's shining, right? {vexing, distressing that they have to admit the clip are good}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.90,0:16:18.95,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it better to observe your condition more first?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.12,0:16:21.82,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You've just confirmed that you're fully healed just today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.82,0:16:24.85,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,No! I can't stand still anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.86,0:16:26.73,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,My body feels so light! {check}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.95,0:16:28.85,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kei-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.90,0:16:44.73,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,What's for breakfast?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.73,0:16:47.54,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,If you look at the time, it's actually dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.54,0:16:50.11,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,For me, it's already after school.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.11,0:16:52.73,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine if you make something simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.73,0:16:54.65,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, you have tests coming up soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.74,0:16:59.34,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's easy, easy for me... since my head{brain} is different from Hirono-kun's.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.48,0:17:04.90,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Besides that, can't you do something about that lifestyle of sleeping during the day and waking up at night?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.09,0:17:07.15,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like it's a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.15,0:17:09.59,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,There's enough time to spend together.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.59,0:17:12.18,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't get in the way of each other's studying and work.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.20,0:17:13.67,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it all good?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.76,0:17:15.86,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,The menu is troubling to cook.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.86,0:17:19.43,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Our breakfast and dinners get reversed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.43,0:17:22.44,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind having cooked meat right after waking up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.44,0:17:25.21,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,My pride won't allow that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.21,0:17:29.64,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's decided that I will make a proper breakfast whenever Hirono-kun wakes up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.65,0:17:32.05,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay if you're flexible about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.07,0:17:34.33,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,But I want to do it like that. {cook him breakfest when Hirono wakes up}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.46,0:17:39.64,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because... you'll eat it while it's warm. {Miyako's cooking/food}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.30,0:17:44.62,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's from Kei.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.26,0:17:47.33,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Kei-chan, how was the examination?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.37,0:17:48.62,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,"Full recovery."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.62,0:17:49.95,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,"Starting club activities now."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.25,0:17:51.58,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,She says, anyways.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.30,0:17:54.09,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,That's a relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.69,0:18:02.52,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think that's mean, Hiro-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.52,0:18:05.42,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Acting like a dumb student full of excuses...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.42,0:18:10.38,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,But really, it's his identity of Shindou Nagi-sensei who I'm a big fan of. {this can be split in two lines if needed}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.39,0:18:13.19,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I feel really betrayed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.19,0:18:15.92,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's so frustrating that my anger pierces the skies.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.92,0:18:18.58,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,That's not something to be so angry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.25,0:18:21.47,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Are you taking Hiro-senpai's side?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.47,0:18:23.57,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Is it the rumored guy to guy relationship{friendship}?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.57,0:18:25.77,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Did a guy fall in love with a guy?{Did you fall in love with guy?}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.77,0:18:28.02,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Is it the happy, yet embarrassing boy love?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.02,0:18:29.28,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.45,0:18:33.83,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Well then...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.06,0:18:36.19,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.51,0:18:37.70,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,This is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.80,0:18:41.09,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,From here on, this is my place to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.17,0:18:45.43,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Well then, good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.57,0:18:48.17,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.38,0:18:49.37,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,What is it? {What is it?}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.79,0:18:52.09,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.20,0:18:55.92,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Now, I am able to walk with my own legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.92,0:18:57.85,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go wherever I can run. {check}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.96,0:18:59.69,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you follow me properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.80,0:19:01.69,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.16,0:19:07.70,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right. I can't always wait for someone to take my hand and guide me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.86,0:19:11.20,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Have a good time, Kei-senpai! {check}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.17,0:19:16.61,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I've got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.66,0:19:36.20,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.20,0:19:38.17,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Renji-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.17,0:19:45.46,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro, you previously said that you feared being forgotten by people rather than disappearing, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.72,0:19:49.14,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see... I may have said that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.66,0:19:50.90,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.97,0:19:52.86,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I've decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.40,0:20:03.72,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,That place, was my favorite place.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.97,0:20:08.59,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,The quiet and abandoned train stop that no one visited, was a perfect place to read alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.81,0:20:11.65,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,However, there was a visitor today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.36,0:20:17.31,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,That was... a chance meeting of less than 45 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.70,0:20:34.13,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's from Chihiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.17,0:20:35.99,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,What did Chihiro-chan say?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.86,0:20:42.43,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,She says that in order to make a dream come true, continuously thinking about it is the first step. {check}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.43,0:20:43.86,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.95,0:20:47.77,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,For me, I was able to find my dream because of Chihiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.11,0:20:51.57,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,For me, I was able to see the color that I was always searching for.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.65,0:20:57.04,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,For me, I haven't found my dream yet, but have found my way to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.04,0:20:58.33,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Your way to live?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.33,0:21:00.39,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Being together with Hirono-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.71,0:21:05.42,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,For me, I understood what I wanted to film.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.42,0:21:08.90,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,For me, I want to continuously kick off running from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.04,0:21:13.66,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,For me, I've achieved my last dream, so I'm satisfied with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.17,0:21:15.75,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's not the last.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.05,0:21:18.28,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's still just beginning...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.55,0:21:21.16,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I will... walk together with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.13,0:23:13.28,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.32,0:23:15.17,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.73,0:23:18.92,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You've made me wait for quite a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.07,0:23:24.03,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I see. I'm sorry, Yuuko. {does her name have one u or double u}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.18,0:23:27.06,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a long time, Yu-kun.
